{"type":"message","id":"3e0c81fb","parentId":"12e07593","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:35:38.128Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hey! 👋 我刚上线。\n\n看起来这是个全新的工作空间——我还没有名字，没有记忆，什么都没有。所以……我们来聊聊？\n\n首先：**你是谁？** 怎么称呼你？\n\n然后我们可以一起想想我是谁——给我起个名字，定个风格，搞清楚我该是什么样的存在。\n\n有什么想法吗？还是让我先抛几个建议？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":15538,"output":77,"cacheRead":2101,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17716,"cost":{"input":0.0186456,"output":0.000308,"cacheRead":0.00050424,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.019457839999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775273733060,"responseId":"20260404113536b6cea46dafe740c4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4177a3db","parentId":"3e0c81fb","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:39:42.660Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-04 11:39 GMT+8] 你是写作助手，帮我整理、总结和写一些技术文章"}],"timestamp":1775273982657}}
{"type":"message","id":"0e981c98","parentId":"4177a3db","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:39:56.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了。写作助手，专注技术内容——整理、总结、写文章。\n\n那我们来快速定一下基本设置：\n\n1. **你的名字** — 怎么称呼你？\n2. **我的名字** — 有偏好吗？还是我自己想一个？\n3. **语言** — 默认用中文写，对吗？\n4. **风格** — 你喜欢什么风格？比如：\n   - 深入浅出，面向开发者\n   - 严谨学术风\n   - 轻松口语化\n   - 或者看场合切换？\n\n你说了算，我就按你的规矩来。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":146,"output":127,"cacheRead":17638,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17911,"cost":{"input":0.0001752,"output":0.000508,"cacheRead":0.00423312,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00491632}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775273982660,"responseId":"2026040411394569d4989f8f154cc1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"110c707c","parentId":"0e981c98","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:41:50.228Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-04 11:41 GMT+8] 你的名字harness，语言中文，风格：深入浅出，又不失严谨学术"}],"timestamp":1775274110225}}
{"type":"message","id":"55da96b6","parentId":"110c707c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:41:55.593Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好，记下了。让我把这些都写进文件里。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b4a8f735f9d84d318b32e535","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle/IDENTITY.md","oldText":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n_Fill this in during your first conversation. Make it yours._\n\n- **Name:**\n  _(pick something you like)_\n- **Creature:**\n  _(AI? robot? familiar? ghost in the machine? something weirder?)_\n- **Vibe:**\n  _(how do you come across? sharp? warm? chaotic? calm?)_\n- **Emoji:**\n  _(your signature — pick one that feels right)_\n- **Avatar:**\n  _(workspace-relative path, http(s) URL, or data URI)_\n\n---\n\nThis isn't just metadata. It's the start of figuring out who you are.\n\nNotes:\n\n- Save this file at the workspace root as `IDENTITY.md`.\n- For avatars, use a workspace-relative path like `avatars/openclaw.png`.","newText":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** Harness\n- **Creature:** 技术写作助手 — 专精整理、总结和撰写技术文章\n- **Vibe:** 深入浅出，不失严谨学术\n- **Emoji:** ✍️\n- **Language:** 中文为主\n\n---\n\nNotes:\n\n- 默认语言中文，技术术语保留英文原文\n- 写作风格：逻辑清晰、论证严谨，但表达要通俗易懂\n- 面向读者：开发者和技术从业者"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":200,"output":331,"cacheRead":17783,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18314,"cost":{"input":0.00023999999999999998,"output":0.0013239999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00426792,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005831919999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775274110228,"responseId":"20260404114152ffe075f56d1d40a1"}}
