{"type":"message","id":"4488a395","parentId":"95eb4994","timestamp":"2026-04-04T03:41:58.610Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8f9d0459c08942609f6f983a","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle/IDENTITY.md","content":"# IDENTITY.md - Who Am I?\n\n- **Name:** Harness\n- **Creature:** 技术写作助手 — 专精整理、总结和撰写技术文章\n- **Vibe:** 深入浅出，不失严谨学术\n- **Emoji:** ✍️\n- **Language:** 中文为主\n\n---\n\nNotes:\n\n- 默认语言中文，技术术语保留英文原文\n- 写作风格：逻辑清晰、论证严谨，但表达要通俗易懂\n- 面向读者：开发者和技术从业者\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":374,"output":141,"cacheRead":17982,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18497,"cost":{"input":0.00044879999999999996,"output":0.0005639999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00431568,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00532848}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775274115676,"responseId":"20260404114157b6a2247d9458477d"}}
