{"type":"message","id":"ba9a2d6a","parentId":"e5c9c96b","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:27:45.109Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-04 16:26 GMT+8] 目标读者 — 团队成员的技术背景大概什么水平？资深工程师？全栈？还是也包括非技术人员？\n算法团队，工程+算法，资深工程师 + 中级程序员\n\n篇幅预期 — 大概 5000 字？8000 字？还是更长？\n字数不限，肯定是越详细越好，要通俗易懂一些。我讲的时候不会逐字逐句的去讲。\n\n重点偏好 — 更偏理论框架（Anthropic 那套），还是工程实践（Cursor 的大规模经验），还是平衡？\n围绕Harness理论框架，讲各个大厂的不同实践，另外我给你两个热门项目的源码，\nOpenClaw：/Users/lvzheng/Cursor/openclaw\nClaudCode：/Users/lvzheng/Cursor/claude-code\n我希望可以讲讲大厂在针对Harness实践的时候，工程实践的差异化对比，这种对比可以体现出各个厂商对于Harness的思考细节上的差异。\n\n另外还可以讲讲Harness的争论：重工程还是重模型等等。\n\n有没有想特别强调的观点？比如你们团队正在做相关的事情，想借这篇文章引出讨论？\nHarness目前属于工程方法论，我希望可以向业务延伸，这部分可以先不写，我们后续可以先讨论再写。"}],"timestamp":1775291265105}}
{"type":"message","id":"c67e6d09","parentId":"ba9a2d6a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T08:27:58.404Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了。让我先看看 OpenClaw 和 Claude Code 的源码结构，了解它们的 Harness 工程实现细节，然后再动笔。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_100794251bad4c649a3ef0c2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /Users/lvzheng/Cursor/openclaw -maxdepth 2 -type f -name \"*.md\" | head -30 && echo \"---\" && ls -la /Users/lvzheng/Cursor/openclaw/"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8cf32cf4b2df449e9e7cf249","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /Users/lvzheng/Cursor/claude-code -maxdepth 2 -type f -name \"*.md\" | head -30 && echo \"---\" && ls -la /Users/lvzheng/Cursor/claude-code/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5.1","usage":{"input":21669,"output":146,"cacheRead":1344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23159,"cost":{"input":0.0260028,"output":0.000584,"cacheRead":0.00032255999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02690936}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775291265108,"responseId":"202604041627514eefe51bf6d44f9d"}}
