{"type":"message","id":"ab10f55a","parentId":"1b6b2bbe","timestamp":"2026-04-04T12:12:05.652Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_759ccbbb0f4d4ef5ab659fc8","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Pattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 647:\n  真正能用起来\"的工程问题。\n\n过去一年，Anthropic、Cursor、OpenAI、Google 等头部玩家在 Harness Engineering 方面展开了密集的工程探索。他们的实践各有侧重，底层模式\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 2750:\n  gineering 所关注的问题域。\n\nAnthropic 在多篇文章中系统阐述了长时间运行代理面临的三个根本挑战。这三个挑战构成了 Harness Engineering 的核心设计约束，也是后续各家实践的出发点。\n\n### \n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 3241:\n  。但长时间任务需要跨会话的持续状态。\n\nAnthropic 提出了**结构化工件（Structured Artifacts）**方案：把关键状态写成文件（如 `claude-progress.txt`），新会话读取它快速理解工作进展。这可以被视为 Harness Engineering 中\"状态持久化\"的一种实践。\n\n这带来了第二个工程问题\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 3822:\n  不同角度的回应。\n\n---\n\n## 二、Anthropic：模型驱动的 Harness Engineering\n\n### 2.1 理论框架：Workflows vs \n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 4331:\n  时，才需要第三步——真正的自主代理。\n\nAnthropic 没有使用\"Harness\"这个词，但他们所描述的这些系统——控制流编排、工具调度、上下文管理——正是 Harness Engineering 的核心关注点。\n\n### 2.2 三代理架构：Plan\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 4512:\n  g-Running Apps》中（注意，Anthropic 在这篇文章标题中直接使用了\"Harness\"一词），Anthropic 提出了一个受 GAN 启发的系统，直接回应了\"问题\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 5123:\n  # 2.3 Opus 4.6 的冲击\n\nAnthropic 最新的 Opus 4.6 模型大幅缓解了上下文焦虑，甚至可以移除 Sprint 结构，简化 Harness。\n\n但这并不意味着\"不需要 Harness Engineering\"，而是说它\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 5622:\n  Claude Code 的实现可以看作 Anthropic Harness Engineering 思想的\"编码领域特化版\"。\n\n#### 回应上下文腐烂\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 17436:\n  AGENTS.md\n\nOpenAI 和 Anthropic 都采用 AGENTS.md，这正在成为一个事实标准。它解决了跨 Harness Engineering 实现的兼容性问题——不同的系统可以用同一个配置文件理解\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 21133:\n  向。\n\n---\n\n## 参考来源\n\n- Anthropic: Building Effective Agents, Effective Harnesses for Long-Running Agents, Effective Context Engineering for AI Agents, Harness Design for Long-Running Apps\n- Cursor: \n\nPattern [多代理.*结构] at 20022:\n  ing 协作？** 比如，训练时直接包含多代理协调、结构化工件读写等场景？\n5. **Harness Engineering 如何向业务"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":68,"aggregated":"Pattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 647:\n  真正能用起来\"的工程问题。\n\n过去一年，Anthropic、Cursor、OpenAI、Google 等头部玩家在 Harness Engineering 方面展开了密集的工程探索。他们的实践各有侧重，底层模式\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 2750:\n  gineering 所关注的问题域。\n\nAnthropic 在多篇文章中系统阐述了长时间运行代理面临的三个根本挑战。这三个挑战构成了 Harness Engineering 的核心设计约束，也是后续各家实践的出发点。\n\n### \n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 3241:\n  。但长时间任务需要跨会话的持续状态。\n\nAnthropic 提出了**结构化工件（Structured Artifacts）**方案：把关键状态写成文件（如 `claude-progress.txt`），新会话读取它快速理解工作进展。这可以被视为 Harness Engineering 中\"状态持久化\"的一种实践。\n\n这带来了第二个工程问题\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 3822:\n  不同角度的回应。\n\n---\n\n## 二、Anthropic：模型驱动的 Harness Engineering\n\n### 2.1 理论框架：Workflows vs \n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 4331:\n  时，才需要第三步——真正的自主代理。\n\nAnthropic 没有使用\"Harness\"这个词，但他们所描述的这些系统——控制流编排、工具调度、上下文管理——正是 Harness Engineering 的核心关注点。\n\n### 2.2 三代理架构：Plan\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 4512:\n  g-Running Apps》中（注意，Anthropic 在这篇文章标题中直接使用了\"Harness\"一词），Anthropic 提出了一个受 GAN 启发的系统，直接回应了\"问题\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 5123:\n  # 2.3 Opus 4.6 的冲击\n\nAnthropic 最新的 Opus 4.6 模型大幅缓解了上下文焦虑，甚至可以移除 Sprint 结构，简化 Harness。\n\n但这并不意味着\"不需要 Harness Engineering\"，而是说它\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 5622:\n  Claude Code 的实现可以看作 Anthropic Harness Engineering 思想的\"编码领域特化版\"。\n\n#### 回应上下文腐烂\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 17436:\n  AGENTS.md\n\nOpenAI 和 Anthropic 都采用 AGENTS.md，这正在成为一个事实标准。它解决了跨 Harness Engineering 实现的兼容性问题——不同的系统可以用同一个配置文件理解\n\nPattern [Anthropic.*Harness] at 21133:\n  向。\n\n---\n\n## 参考来源\n\n- Anthropic: Building Effective Agents, Effective Harnesses for Long-Running Agents, Effective Context Engineering for AI Agents, Harness Design for Long-Running Apps\n- Cursor: \n\nPattern [多代理.*结构] at 20022:\n  ing 协作？** 比如，训练时直接包含多代理协调、结构化工件读写等场景？\n5. **Harness Engineering 如何向业务","cwd":"/Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775304725651}}
{"type":"message","id":"3928340b","parentId":"ab10f55a","timestamp":"2026-04-04T12:12:09.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9ec24a152e7544d3b1b2d913","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle && python3 -c \"\nwith open('Harness技术实践对比.md', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\nimport re\n\n# Check for '必然' and '必须' in context of multi-agent\nfor pattern in ['多代理.*必然', '必然.*多代理', '多代理.*必须', '必须.*多代理', '硬层级.*必须', '必须.*硬层级']:\n    matches = [(m.start(), content[max(0,m.start()-30):m.end()+50]) for m in re.finditer(pattern, content)]\n    if matches:\n        for pos, ctx in matches:\n            print(f'Pattern [{pattern}] at {pos}:')\n            print(f'  {ctx}')\n            print()\n\n# Check for Orchestrator distinction\nif 'Orchestrator' in content or 'orchestrator' in content:\n    print('Orchestrator found in text')\nelse:\n    print('Orchestrator NOT found - should add distinction')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":875,"output":236,"cacheRead":96936,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98047,"cost":{"input":0.00105,"output":0.000944,"cacheRead":0.02326464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02525864}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775304725654,"responseId":"20260404201207901f03652e1f434d"}}
