{"type":"message","id":"494b9ed7","parentId":"47b51e73","timestamp":"2026-04-04T13:41:53.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"ADK 章节全部删除了，包括：\n- 第五章整章\n- 对比表中的两行（核心挑战表 + 安全策略表）\n- 总结段落中的 Google ADK 条目\n- 参考来源中的 Google 条目\n- 所有后续章节编号顺延（六→五，七→六，以此类推）\n\nCodex 的资料你找到后发给我，我来补充第四章。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":713,"output":88,"cacheRead":115474,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116275,"cost":{"input":0.0008556,"output":0.000352,"cacheRead":0.027713759999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.028921359999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775310107842,"responseId":"202604042141497c24142b8ed64e05"}}
