{"type":"message","id":"1c38499e","parentId":"021601b1","timestamp":"2026-04-04T13:45:47.119Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在更新横向对比表中的 Codex 行，以及总结部分："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_68ffd5a3ca8a4d79bddfe2ce","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nwith open('Harness技术实践对比.md', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\nchanges = 0\n\n# Update comparison table - Codex row\nold_row = '| **OpenAI Codex** | 任务级 VM 隔离，每个任务干净开始，问题在架构层面不发生 | 每次从仓库快照开始，不需要跨会话记忆（代价：放弃跨任务积累） | 可验证输出（终端日志 + 测试），交还用户判断 |'\nnew_row = '| **OpenAI Codex** | API 原生 Prompt Caching（静态前置）+ Compaction 端点（加密 latent understanding） | 无跨会话记忆设计，单任务内通过加密压缩保留潜在理解 | 无内置评估机制，依赖用户判断和可验证输出 |'\nassert old_row in content, 'Codex row not found!'\ncontent = content.replace(old_row, new_row, 1)\nchanges += 1\n\n# Update security table - Codex row\nold_sec = '| **OpenAI Codex** | 云端运行 | 沙箱隔离 + 可验证输出 | 隔离 + 审计 |'\nnew_sec = '| **Codex CLI** | 本地运行（API 调用云端模型） | 分层沙箱：Codex 工具沙箱化，MCP/第三方工具由提供方负责 | 明确划分安全责任边界 |'\nassert old_sec in content, 'Codex security row not found!'\ncontent = content.replace(old_sec, new_sec, 1)\nchanges += 1\n\n# Update summary paragraph\nold_sum = '- **OpenAI**：产品化优先，标准化，云沙箱'\nnew_sum = '- **OpenAI Codex**：API 原生化优先，让模型 API 为 Harness 服务，Prompt Caching + Compaction 端点'\nassert old_sum in content, 'Codex summary not found!'\ncontent = content.replace(old_sum, new_sum, 1)\nchanges += 1\n\n# Update the \"消除挑战\" paragraph in section 8.3 table if it still references old Codex approach\nold_table = '| **上下文压缩** | 必需（上下文窗口小） | 可选（上下文窗口大） | ↓ 降低 |'\n# This should still be fine, no change needed\n\n# Update references - add the new article\nold_ref = '- OpenAI: Introducing Codex, Codex Developer Documentation'\nnew_ref = '- OpenAI: Unrolling the Codex Agent Loop, Introducing Codex, Codex Developer Documentation, Codex CLI (https://github.com/openai/codex)'\nassert old_ref in content, 'OpenAI ref not found!'\ncontent = content.replace(old_ref, new_ref, 1)\nchanges += 1\n\nwith open('Harness技术实践对比.md', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(content)\nprint(f'Done - {changes} updates')\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":2470,"output":680,"cacheRead":121528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":124678,"cost":{"input":0.002964,"output":0.0027199999999999998,"cacheRead":0.029166719999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.034850719999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775310335675,"responseId":"20260404214537bf66579b5fc94c66"}}
