{"type":"message","id":"42457bef","parentId":"53a02736","timestamp":"2026-04-04T14:01:33.448Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"加了两处：\n\n1. **Anthropic 文章时间线表格** — 四篇文章按时间排列，从 2024 年底的框架定义到 2026 年 3 月的三代理架构和 Reset vs Compaction 的工程决策\n2. **渐进式模型加了行内注释** — 每一层右侧用箭头标注含义，和刚才解释 Augmented LLM 的方式一致\n\n这样 Anthropic 在 Harness 方向上的发展脉络就清晰了：先定义框架 → 再分析核心问题（上下文、长时间运行）→ 最后提出具体架构方案。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":506,"output":120,"cacheRead":130851,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131477,"cost":{"input":0.0006072,"output":0.00047999999999999996,"cacheRead":0.03140424,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.032491439999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775311286214,"responseId":"2026040422012821829c87c4814cad"}}
{"type":"message","id":"4991e0c6","parentId":"42457bef","timestamp":"2026-04-04T14:03:47.349Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-04 22:03 GMT+8] Sprint 是什么？Sprint结构？Sprint契约？"}],"timestamp":1775311427344}}
{"type":"message","id":"06b07943","parentId":"4991e0c6","timestamp":"2026-04-04T14:04:03.435Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sprint 在 Anthropic 的文章中是一个**限定范围的工作周期**概念，借用自敏捷开发中的术语。让我把这几个相关概念一次性讲清楚，然后看看文章中是否需要补充：\n\n**Sprint（冲刺）**：一段限定范围的工作周期。Generator 不是一口气做完所有事，而是把任务拆成多个 Sprint，每个 Sprint 只做一部分。\n\n**Sprint 结构**：指整个任务被拆分成多个 Sprint 的组织方式——什么时候开始新 Sprint、每个 Sprint 的范围多大、Sprint 之间如何交接。\n\n**Sprint 契约（Sprint Contract）**：这是最关键的设计。在每个 Sprint 开始之前，Planner 和 Generator/Evaluator 要协商一个\"完成标准\"——这个 Sprint 做什么、做到什么程度算\"完成\"。这避免了评估时的模糊标准——Evaluator 不是主观判断\"好不好\"，而是对照契约检查\"达没达到约定标准\"。\n\n简单类比：\n- Sprint = 一场比赛\n- Sprint 结构 = 赛程安排（几场比赛、每场跑多远）\n- Sprint 契约 = 每场比赛的达标线（跑完这段算赢）\n\n文章中 Sprint 契约已经有括号解释了，但 Sprint 本身第一次出现时没有。我加上："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c346762985004c6ba21ef4c9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nwith open('Harness技术实践对比.md', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# Sprint structure first mention - in Opus 4.6 section\nold1 = 'Sprint 结构可以简化甚至移除'\nnew1 = 'Sprint（冲刺，即限定范围的工作周期）结构可以简化甚至移除'\nassert old1 in content\ncontent = content.replace(old1, new1)\n\n# Sprint granularity in table\nold2 = 'Sprint 粒度可变粗'\nnew2 = 'Sprint（工作周期）粒度可变粗'\nassert old2 in content\ncontent = content.replace(old2, new2)\n\n# Sprint contract in 2.2 already has explanation, but let's also add context to the table row\nold3 = '- **Sprint 契约机制**：每个 Sprint（冲刺，即一段限定范围的工作周期）开始前协商\"完成\"标准，避免评估时的模糊标准'\nnew3 = '- **Sprint 契约机制**：每个 Sprint（冲刺，即一段限定范围的工作周期）开始前协商\"完成\"标准——明确这个周期做什么、做到什么程度算完成，避免评估时的模糊标准'\nassert old3 in content\ncontent = content.replace(old3, new3)\n\nwith open('Harness技术实践对比.md', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(content)\nprint('Done')\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":187,"output":603,"cacheRead":131356,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132146,"cost":{"input":0.00022439999999999998,"output":0.002412,"cacheRead":0.031525439999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03416183999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775311427348,"responseId":"2026040422035245f8a5d333ff4a76"}}
