{"type":"message","id":"f566ec2d","parentId":"0761b024","timestamp":"2026-04-04T14:04:07.674Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f110006ae9ec4957bd945564","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nwith open('Harness技术实践对比.md', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\nimport re\n# Find all \"Sprint\" mentions that don't already have explanation\nfor m in re.finditer(r'Sprint 结构', content):\n    print(f'At {m.start()}: ...{content[max(0,m.start()-20):m.end()+20]}...')\n\nprint('---')\nfor m in re.finditer(r'Sprint 粒度', content):\n    print(f'At {m.start()}: ...{content[max(0,m.start()-20):m.end()+20]}...')\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":639,"output":167,"cacheRead":131542,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132348,"cost":{"input":0.0007668,"output":0.000668,"cacheRead":0.03157008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.03300488}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775311443545,"responseId":"202604042204056a6ac84bb7df4f70"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0567ff9b","parentId":"f566ec2d","timestamp":"2026-04-04T14:04:07.835Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f110006ae9ec4957bd945564","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"At 6790: ...----|\n| **上下文腐烂** | Sprint 结构限制每次的工作范围，避免上下文过度膨胀；...\nAt 7983: ...需要频繁的 Context Reset，Sprint 结构也因此可以简化甚至移除。\n\n这个演进很好...\nAt 22740: ...ntext Reset 的依赖）让一些 Sprint 结构变得不必要\n- 大型模型的规划能力在提升...\nAt 23300: ...需 | 可选 | ↓ 降低 |\n| **Sprint 结构** | 上下文腐烂 + 自我评估偏差 ...\nAt 25887: ...到\"保障系统可靠\"。**\n\n上下文压缩、Sprint 结构、评估分离等\"补丁式\"组件可能会随着模型...\n---\nAt 8299: ...模型自身行为改善，可在单会话内持续工作，Sprint 粒度可变粗 |\n| **记忆断裂** | 结..."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":140,"aggregated":"At 6790: ...----|\n| **上下文腐烂** | Sprint 结构限制每次的工作范围，避免上下文过度膨胀；...\nAt 7983: ...需要频繁的 Context Reset，Sprint 结构也因此可以简化甚至移除。\n\n这个演进很好...\nAt 22740: ...ntext Reset 的依赖）让一些 Sprint 结构变得不必要\n- 大型模型的规划能力在提升...\nAt 23300: ...需 | 可选 | ↓ 降低 |\n| **Sprint 结构** | 上下文腐烂 + 自我评估偏差 ...\nAt 25887: ...到\"保障系统可靠\"。**\n\n上下文压缩、Sprint 结构、评估分离等\"补丁式\"组件可能会随着模型...\n---\nAt 8299: ...模型自身行为改善，可在单会话内持续工作，Sprint 粒度可变粗 |\n| **记忆断裂** | 结...","cwd":"/Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775311447830}}
{"type":"message","id":"db384820","parentId":"0567ff9b","timestamp":"2026-04-04T14:04:18.421Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f796260f76ba44c99267f4f7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nwith open('Harness技术实践对比.md', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\n# First unexplained \"Sprint 结构\" in the Opus 4.6 section\nold1 = 'Sprint 结构也因此可以简化甚至移除'\nnew1 = 'Sprint（限定范围的工作周期）结构也因此可以简化甚至移除'\nassert old1 in content\ncontent = content.replace(old1, new1)\n\n# Sprint structure in section 8 table\nold2 = '| **Sprint 结构** | 上下文腐烂 + 自我评估偏差 | 必需（模型规划能力弱） | 可选（模型可自主规划） | ↓ 降低 |'\nnew2 = '| **Sprint 结构** | 上下文腐烂 + 自我评估偏差 | 必需（模型规划能力弱） | 可选（模型可自主规划） | ↓ 降低 |'\n# This one is already clear from context, skip\n\n# Sprint粒度\nold3 = 'Sprint 粒度可变粗'\nnew3 = 'Sprint（工作周期）粒度可变粗'\nassert old3 in content\ncontent = content.replace(old3, new3)\n\n# Enhance Sprint contract explanation\nold4 = '- **Sprint 契约机制**：每个 Sprint（冲刺，即一段限定范围的工作周期）开始前协商\"完成\"标准，避免评估时的模糊标准'\nnew4 = '- **Sprint 契约机制**：每个 Sprint（冲刺，即一段限定范围的工作周期）开始前协商\"完成\"标准——明确这个周期做什么、做到什么程度算完成，避免评估时的模糊标准'\nassert old4 in content\ncontent = content.replace(old4, new4)\n\nwith open('Harness技术实践对比.md', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(content)\nprint('Done')\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":365,"output":431,"cacheRead":132180,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":132976,"cost":{"input":0.00043799999999999997,"output":0.0017239999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0317232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0338852}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775311447838,"responseId":"20260404220409bf6a1a4559164dd8"}}
