{"type":"message","id":"8f183e26","parentId":"d48ae662","timestamp":"2026-04-04T14:27:55.792Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6bc509a1cf9447309b88587f","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"599:| **Anthropic（理论）** | Sprint 分块限制工作范围；Compaction 压缩继续；Context Reset 彻底重置 | 结构化 artifact（`progress.txt`）进行跨会话交接 | Planner-Generator-Evaluator 分离；Generator 先自评，Evaluator 再独立验收 |"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":13,"aggregated":"599:| **Anthropic（理论）** | Sprint 分块限制工作范围；Compaction 压缩继续；Context Reset 彻底重置 | 结构化 artifact（`progress.txt`）进行跨会话交接 | Planner-Generator-Evaluator 分离；Generator 先自评，Evaluator 再独立验收 |","cwd":"/Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775312875789}}
{"type":"message","id":"7ee0226b","parentId":"8f183e26","timestamp":"2026-04-04T14:28:01.118Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b5bbce60655e4df699ee7555","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nwith open('Harness技术实践对比.md', 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    content = f.read()\n\nold = '| **Anthropic（理论）** | Sprint 分块限制工作范围；Compaction 压缩继续；Context Reset 彻底重置 |'\nnew = '| **Anthropic（理论）** | Planner 将大任务拆分为小工作周期（Sprint），每个 Sprint 内上下文可控；Compaction 压缩继续；Context Reset 彻底重置 |'\nassert old in content\ncontent = content.replace(old, new)\n\nwith open('Harness技术实践对比.md', 'w', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n    f.write(content)\nprint('Done')\nPYEOF"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":113,"output":187,"cacheRead":133926,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134226,"cost":{"input":0.0001356,"output":0.000748,"cacheRead":0.032142239999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.033025839999999994}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775312875793,"responseId":"202604042227578bbe47cbf8184e2c"}}
