{"type":"message","id":"56beee41","parentId":"eec55a86","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:14:44.733Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3c95c25881834022bf4338dd","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle/Harness技术实践对比.md","offset":131,"limit":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":62,"output":41,"cacheRead":55848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55951,"cost":{"input":0.00007439999999999999,"output":0.000164,"cacheRead":0.013403519999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013641919999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775315681589,"responseId":"2026040423144499e1c74a6b964aa3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"8349d3ba","parentId":"56beee41","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:14:44.758Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_3c95c25881834022bf4338dd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### 补充说明:Harness Engineering ≠ Workflow Orchestrator\n\n一个容易混淆的问题是:Harness Engineering 和传统的 Workflow Orchestrator(如 Airflow、Temporal)有什么区别?\n\n两者都涉及\"编排\",但本质不同:\n\n- **Workflow Orchestrator** 编排的是**确定性流程**--步骤、分支、重试策略都是预定义的,执行过程可预测\n- **Harness Engineering** 管控的是**非确定性决策**--LLM 的输出不可预测,Harness 的职责是在不确定性中建立可控性\n\n更准确地说,Harness 作为系统的**控制入口(control plane)**,负责调度与约束任务执行过程。它不只是编排步骤,还要管理上下文状态、验证输出质量、处理模型的不确定性。\n\n这也是为什么 Harness Engineering 的关注点--上下文腐烂、记忆断裂、自我评估偏差--在传统编排系统中不存在。传统系统不需要担心\"编排器看不清前面做了什么\",但 LLM 需要。\n\n---\n\n\n[638 more lines in file. Use offset=146 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775315684756}}
{"type":"message","id":"57702101","parentId":"8349d3ba","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:14:50.100Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5434ae12a0dd4ed2aad666d4","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"更准确地说,Harness 是模型推理运行的**工程支撑层**,不是驱动执行的主体,而是让模型能可靠运行的基础设施:保证模型看到的上下文是清晰的、用到的工具是可靠的、产出的结果是可验证的。执行什么、怎么执行,始终是模型的推理在决定;Harness 负责的是--无论模型决定做什么,这件事都能可靠地发生。","oldText":"更准确地说,Harness 作为系统的**控制入口(control plane)**,负责调度与约束任务执行过程。它不只是编排步骤,还要管理上下文状态、验证输出质量、处理模型的不确定性。"}],"path":"/Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle/Harness技术实践对比.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":260,"output":170,"cacheRead":55909,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56339,"cost":{"input":0.000312,"output":0.0006799999999999999,"cacheRead":0.013418159999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014410159999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775315684759,"responseId":"2026040423144756037b6f53c74c6f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"41bd3360","parentId":"57702101","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:14:50.147Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5434ae12a0dd4ed2aad666d4","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle/Harness技术实践对比.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 136 \n 137 - **Workflow Orchestrator** 编排的是**确定性流程**--步骤、分支、重试策略都是预定义的,执行过程可预测\n 138 - **Harness Engineering** 管控的是**非确定性决策**--LLM 的输出不可预测,Harness 的职责是在不确定性中建立可控性\n 139 \n-140 更准确地说,Harness 作为系统的**控制入口(control plane)**,负责调度与约束任务执行过程。它不只是编排步骤,还要管理上下文状态、验证输出质量、处理模型的不确定性。\n+140 更准确地说,Harness 是模型推理运行的**工程支撑层**,不是驱动执行的主体,而是让模型能可靠运行的基础设施:保证模型看到的上下文是清晰的、用到的工具是可靠的、产出的结果是可验证的。执行什么、怎么执行,始终是模型的推理在决定;Harness 负责的是--无论模型决定做什么,这件事都能可靠地发生。\n 141 \n 142 这也是为什么 Harness Engineering 的关注点--上下文腐烂、记忆断裂、自我评估偏差--在传统编排系统中不存在。传统系统不需要担心\"编排器看不清前面做了什么\",但 LLM 需要。\n 143 \n 144 ---\n     ...","firstChangedLine":140},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775315690144}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce5335a0","parentId":"41bd3360","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:14:53.112Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"改了。新的表述更准确地传达了\"模型驱动、Harness 支撑\"的关系——执行权始终在模型，Harness 是让这件事可靠发生的基础设施。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":204,"output":36,"cacheRead":56168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56408,"cost":{"input":0.0002448,"output":0.000144,"cacheRead":0.013480319999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.013869119999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775315690148,"responseId":"20260404231452e4d2f934cbe24c81"}}
{"type":"message","id":"010b2186","parentId":"ce5335a0","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:15:27.240Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-04 23:15 GMT+8] 是的，“Harness 作为系统的控制入口(control plane),负责调度与约束任务执行过程。它不只是编排步骤,还要管理上下文状态、验证输出质量、处理模型的不确定性。\"，我总觉得这种描述，还是会让人觉得Harness偏向于Worflow执行。"}],"timestamp":1775315727236}}
{"type":"message","id":"49281212","parentId":"010b2186","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:15:33.060Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"对，\"控制入口\"、\"调度\"、\"约束\"这些词确实有 Workflow 的味道——暗示有一个外部系统在\"指挥\"模型。\n\n改后的版本好多了：\"工程支撑层\"、\"模型决定执行什么、Harness 保证可靠发生\"——把主动权明确给了模型，Harness 是配角而不是导演。\n\n这篇文章关于这个定位其实反复强调了多次（\"推理驱动不是流程驱动\"、\"驾驶员/安全带\"类比、Coordinator 三层架构中的\"模型只管推理和决策，Harness 只管执行和编排\"），现在这段也统一了，整体口径一致了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":145,"output":118,"cacheRead":56371,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56634,"cost":{"input":0.000174,"output":0.000472,"cacheRead":0.013529039999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01417504}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775315727239,"responseId":"202604042315314c586ee276104f15"}}
{"type":"message","id":"db60d110","parentId":"49281212","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:22:35.471Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Sat 2026-04-04 23:22 GMT+8] \"生成器-评估器分离(Generator-Evaluator Separation)--Anthropic 在其文章中对此有系统性阐述。两个独立的模型实例,一个干活,一个验收。这启发了 GAN(Generative Adversarial Network,生成对抗网络)式的多代理架构\", \"在《Harness Design for Long-Running Apps》中(注意,Anthropic 在这篇文章标题中直接使用了\"Harness\"一词),Anthropic 提出了一个受 GAN 启发的系统,直接回应了\"问题三角\"。到底是谁启发了谁？"}],"timestamp":1775316155468}}
{"type":"message","id":"d6f06ee4","parentId":"db60d110","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:22:43.840Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，这里有矛盾。\n\n实际情况是：**Generator-Evaluator 分离是 Anthropic 在《Harness Design for Long-Running Apps》中提出的，同时 Anthropic 在这篇文章中说这个设计\"受 GAN 启发\"**。所以逻辑链是：\n\nGAN → 启发了 Anthropic → Anthropic 提出了 Generator-Evaluator 分离\n\n而不是反过来。文章现在的写法确实容易让人读成\"Generator-Evaluator 分离启发了 GAN\"。我来修正："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_20880aa0b8754deba1bcc99c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle && grep -n \"生成器-评估器分离\" Harness技术实践对比.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":285,"output":141,"cacheRead":56515,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56941,"cost":{"input":0.00034199999999999996,"output":0.0005639999999999999,"cacheRead":0.013563599999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014469599999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775316155470,"responseId":"20260404232240d8848534a4834e66"}}
{"type":"message","id":"596a3aad","parentId":"d6f06ee4","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:22:43.870Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_20880aa0b8754deba1bcc99c","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"123:一种被广泛采纳的解决之道是 **生成器-评估器分离(Generator-Evaluator Separation)**--Anthropic 在其文章中对此有系统性阐述。两个独立的模型实例,一个干活,一个验收。这启发了 GAN(Generative Adversarial Network,生成对抗网络)式的多代理架构1--通过生成与评估的对抗关系来提升输出质量。\n196:| **自我评估偏差** | 生成器-评估器分离,两个独立实例各司其职 |"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":13,"aggregated":"123:一种被广泛采纳的解决之道是 **生成器-评估器分离(Generator-Evaluator Separation)**--Anthropic 在其文章中对此有系统性阐述。两个独立的模型实例,一个干活,一个验收。这启发了 GAN(Generative Adversarial Network,生成对抗网络)式的多代理架构1--通过生成与评估的对抗关系来提升输出质量。\n196:| **自我评估偏差** | 生成器-评估器分离,两个独立实例各司其职 |","cwd":"/Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775316163866}}
{"type":"message","id":"74178c21","parentId":"596a3aad","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:22:49.313Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9ed2d96d63514066af2dac6c","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"一种被广泛采纳的解决之道是 **生成器-评估器分离(Generator-Evaluator Separation)**:两个独立的模型实例,一个负责生成(干活),一个负责验收。这个设计受 GAN(Generative Adversarial Network,生成对抗网络)的启发1--通过生成与评估的对抗关系来提升输出质量。Anthropic 在《Harness Design for Long-Running Apps》中对此有系统性阐述,并将其发展为 Planner-Generator-Evaluator 三代理架构。","oldText":"一种被广泛采纳的解决之道是 **生成器-评估器分离(Generator-Evaluator Separation)**--Anthropic 在其文章中对此有系统性阐述。两个独立的模型实例,一个干活,一个验收。这启发了 GAN(Generative Adversarial Network,生成对抗网络)式的多代理架构1--通过生成与评估的对抗关系来提升输出质量。"}],"path":"/Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle/Harness技术实践对比.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":253,"output":228,"cacheRead":56799,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57280,"cost":{"input":0.0003036,"output":0.0009119999999999999,"cacheRead":0.013631759999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014847359999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775316163871,"responseId":"202604042322460847c69261fd4757"}}
{"type":"message","id":"78cc9f4c","parentId":"74178c21","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:22:49.342Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_9ed2d96d63514066af2dac6c","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in /Users/lvzheng/.openclaw/workspace-assistant-circle/Harness技术实践对比.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 119 ### 1.3 自我评估偏差(Self-Evaluation Bias)\n 120 \n 121 让模型自己评估自己写的代码,天然存在偏差--它会倾向于认为\"我写的没问题\"。学术界通常用 Sycophancy(阿谀顺从)或 Self-Reinforcement Bias 来描述这一现象,其成因不仅包括模型本身的倾向,也包括 RLHF 训练过程中对自身输出产生的高置信度。\n 122 \n-123 一种被广泛采纳的解决之道是 **生成器-评估器分离(Generator-Evaluator Separation)**--Anthropic 在其文章中对此有系统性阐述。两个独立的模型实例,一个干活,一个验收。这启发了 GAN(Generative Adversarial Network,生成对抗网络)式的多代理架构1--通过生成与评估的对抗关系来提升输出质量。\n+123 一种被广泛采纳的解决之道是 **生成器-评估器分离(Generator-Evaluator Separation)**:两个独立的模型实例,一个负责生成(干活),一个负责验收。这个设计受 GAN(Generative Adversarial Network,生成对抗网络)的启发1--通过生成与评估的对抗关系来提升输出质量。Anthropic 在《Harness Design for Long-Running Apps》中对此有系统性阐述,并将其发展为 Planner-Generator-Evaluator 三代理架构。\n 124 \n 125 这带来了第三个工程问题:**如何可靠地验证模型的工作质量?** 这个问题催生了多代理协调、硬层级架构、可观测性等一系列工程实践。\n 126 \n 127 ---\n     ...","firstChangedLine":123},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775316169340}}
{"type":"message","id":"511f6c51","parentId":"78cc9f4c","timestamp":"2026-04-04T15:22:53.126Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"改了。现在逻辑链清晰了：\n\n1. GAN 是已有的概念（生成对抗网络）\n2. Anthropic 受 GAN 启发，提出了 Generator-Evaluator 分离\n3. 在《Harness Design for Long-Running Apps》中进一步发展为三代理架构\n\n不再是\"分离启发了 GAN\"的倒置表述。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":262,"output":72,"cacheRead":57051,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57385,"cost":{"input":0.0003144,"output":0.000288,"cacheRead":0.01369224,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014294639999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775316169343,"responseId":"20260404232251353043c493334bde"}}
